## Key directories

<!-- What lives where. The agent uses this to navigate without grep-walking the tree. -->

- `src/lib/` — shared utilities (date, format, API client)
- `src/components/` — UI components, organized by domain
- `src/hooks/` — custom React hooks
- `apiserver/` — Django backend
- `db/migrations/` — schema changes (numbered, never edit shipped)

## Reusable utilities (DON'T re-invent)

<!-- The agent's primary defense against drift. List the helpers that already exist. See implement-feature skill for why this matters. -->

| Concern | Helper | Lives in |
|---|---|---|
| Permission check | `hasAccess(user, role)` | `@/lib/auth` |
| Debounced input | `useDebounce(value, ms)` | `@/hooks/useDebounce` |
| Date math | `parseDate`, `formatDate` | `@/lib/date` |
| API client | `apiClient` (handles auth + base URL + error mapping) | `@/lib/api` |
| Toast / banner | `useToast()` | `@/hooks/useToast` |

